{"tid":618751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子朗屏邨墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-04-06T05:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T05:20:30.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"938f806b3d1d2515980c6cd5f2ba59ae14ed1460","tid":618751,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T05:12:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180406/photo/bkn-20180406103513517-0406_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180406112523\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180406%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180406103513517-0406_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180406112523&h=97e2ef23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子墮樓亡，警用圍欄及白布遮掩死者遺體。（冼耀華攝）<br />\n<br />\n元朗男子墮樓身亡。早上9時許，一名男子自朗屏邨錦屏樓高處墮下，跌在大廈對開重傷昏迷，救護員接報趕至檢驗證實明顯死亡，警方正在場調查，初步證實死者33歲，正聯絡其家人助查。 <br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線： <br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222 <br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000 <br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288 <br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255 <br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000 <br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281 <br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180406/mobile/bkn-20180406103513517-0406_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180406%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180406103513517-0406_00822_001.html&d=b8ERq2ZtotwSsxfMLDpdgP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=eb17318e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180406/mobile/bkn-20180406103513517-0406_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0728d88831b545eea303598b84e123757c03391a","tid":618751,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T05:13:29.000Z","msg":"真係每日都有人跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc5d979876dec8aab3a01e8f965d586400c734d","tid":618751,"uid":157841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T05:16:54.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8dc0d2f08195af18cfac716c